// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-1099 — Mass File Rename (alphv)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 27d9408f-9861-5412-ba0a-545e7bd22849

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
